resources.description:
This is a guide to the files in the One-shot Data folder.
1. newCOPD 20.xls: Reversed order raw data and payoffs for 40-person one-shot experiments.
2. origCOPD 20.xls: Original order raw data and payoffs for 40-person one-shot experiments.
resources.name: One Shot Data

resources.description:
This is a guide to the files in the Phase 1 Data folder.
1. fix-pha1-raw-data.xls: Raw data in one-zero format for all fixed matched designs.
2. rand-pha1-raw-data.xls: Raw data in one-zero format for all Random matched designs.
3. Ph1-sum-rand.xls: Summary of data (play of A and B) for all random matched designs. Summary is overall and by round for design or session. (Note: DO NOT update the spreadsheet when prompted)
4. Ph1-sum-fix.xls: Summary of data (play of A and B) for all fixed matched designs. Summary is overall and by round for design or session. (Note: DO NOT update the spreadsheet when prompted)
5. Ph1-chi-rand.xls: Chi-squared test results for Random match analysis (table 4).
6. Ph1-chi-fix.xls: Chi-squared test results for Fixed match analysis (table 9).
7. seqresults.xls: Raw data used by other sheets.
8. Seqresam.xls: Raw data used by other sheets.
9. Seqresa0.xls: Raw data used by other sheets.
resources.name: Phase 1

resources.description:
This is a guide to the files in the Phase 2 Data folder.
1. fix-pha2-raw-data.xls: Raw data in one-zero format for all fixed matched designs.
2. rand-pha2-raw-data.xls: Raw data in one-zero format for all Random matched designs.
3. Ph2-sum-rand.xls: Summary of data for all random matched designs (Play of A). Includes Phase 2 data, Phase 1 history and charts for Coord and PD games (Note: DO NOT update the spreadsheet when prompted).
4. Ph2-sum-fix.xls: Summary of data for all fixed matched designs (play of A). Includes Phase 2 data, Phase 1 history and charts for Coord and PD games (Note: DO NOT update the spreadsheet when prompted).
5. phase2-sum: Summary of all Phase2 data (play of A) for ALL designs (table 5).
6. Ph2-chiCOPD-rand.xls: Chi-squared test results for Coordination and PD phase 2 games; random match designs (table 6).
7. Ph2-chiCOPD-fix.xls: Chi-squared test results for Coordination and PD phase 2 games: fixed match analysis (table 11).
resources.name: Phase 2

resources.description:
This is a guide to the files in the Regression folder.
1. Coord-regdata-fix.xls: Regression data for fixed match logit (table 12).
2. Coord-regdata-rand.xls: Regression data for random match logit (table 7).
3. Logit-results-fix.spo: SPSS regression output for fixed match logit (table 12).
3. Logit-results-rand.spo: SPSS regression output for random match logit (table 7).
resources.name: Regression Data

organization.description: Group for Economics data especially that which is [open data](http://opendefinition.org/). This can be any kind of data related to economics from development to finance, and micro to macro. We run an open group policy so anyone can add datasets to this group but we will review datasets added to the group for quality.
organization.title: Economics Datasets
